The perfect spot: on a Sunday afternoon for happy hour after romping through the park on a Monday night for Goulash night (or the trout) (or that bean thing) (and some beers (of which there are like seven on tap which all taste the same but who cares) on your birthday when you need to have, like, a bunch of people meet someplace where some want food, others want drinks, on Sunday nights at 10:30 when they show movies and you can get this bread pudding thing with a strawberry on a winter night for some brandy on a summer night to sit outside and watch people stroll by
